* Timeout\nThresholds
** Purpose
***_ Terminate hung tasks
***_ Prevent resource waste
***_ Allow clean retry or failure
** Configuration
***_ Task > Metric thresholds
***_ Metric: Run duration
***_ Warning: notification threshold
***_ Timeout: termination threshold
** Warning vs Timeout
***_ Warning: alert but continue
***_ Timeout: terminate task
** After Timeout
***_ Status: "Timed Out"
***_ Counts as failed attempt
***_ Triggers retry if attempts remain
***_ Dependent tasks affected
@endmindmap
